H1.text: what are the parts of a domain name called. Domain Label

H2.text: what are the parts of a domain name called. Namespace

H3.text: what are the parts of a domain name called. hostname

A4.text: A domain name consists of one or more parts, technically called labels, that are conventionally concatenated, and delimited by dots, such as example.com.

A5.text: Individual Internet host computers use domain names as host identifiers, also called hostnames.
